PN,37401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,FA warrant to arrest a violent
OL,7,Fschizophrenic man before he killed
OL,8,Fthree people in Nottingham was not
OL,9,Fexecuted by police for months before
OL,10,Fthe attacks in what was described as a
OL,11,F"serious, systemic, operational
OL,12,Ffailure", an inquiry has heard.
OL,14,FValdo Calocane killed University of
OL,15,FNottingham students Barnaby Webber and
OL,16,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and
OL,17,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, 65, and
OL,18,Fattempted to kill three more people in
OL,19,FJune 2023.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,FThe warrant was issued in September
OL,7,F2022, 10 months before the killings,
OL,8,Fat Nottingham Magistrates' Court after
OL,9,FCalocane, who was accused of
OL,10,Fassaulting an emergency worker, did
OL,11,Fnot attend the hearing.
OL,13,FA month before the fatal attacks,
OL,14,FCalocane assaulted two colleagues at a
OL,15,Ffactory in Kegworth, Leicestershire,
OL,16,Fbut he was not arrested by
OL,17,FLeicestershire Police at that time.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,FIn his opening statement on behalf of
OL,7,Fthe relatives of Mr Webber, Miss
OL,8,FO'Malley-Kumar and Mr Coates, Tim
OL,9,FMoloney KC said that any attempt by
OL,10,Fpolice to say arresting Calocane would
OL,11,Fnot have made a difference would be
OL,12,F"cowardly, highly offensive and
OL,13,Finsulting".
OL,15,FHe said: "That warrant was outstanding
OL,16,Ffor 10 months, and Nottinghamshire
OL,17,FPolice did not execute it for 10
OL,18,Fmonths. They just left him out on the
OL,19,Fstreets."
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@JO]wD@JOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,FMr Moloney continued: "Any attempt by
OL,7,Fthe police to say arresting him would
OL,8,Fhave made no difference to what was to
OL,9,Fhappen on June 13 2023, sheltering
OL,10,Fbehind some notion that he may not
OL,11,Fhave been convicted and may not have
OL,12,Freceived a custodial sentence, would
OL,13,Fbe cowardly, highly offensive and
OL,14,Finsulting to the intelligence of the
OL,15,Fbrave families.
OL,26,@nD@WOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,F"If the police do say that executing a
OL,7,Fwarrant for his arrest would have made
OL,8,Fno difference, then the people of
OL,9,FNottinghamshire and Leicestershire
OL,10,Fhave a lot to worry about in relation
OL,11,Fto who is keeping them safe."
OL,13,FJohn Beggs KC, who is representing
OL,14,FNottinghamshire Police in the inquiry,
OL,15,Fsaid the force should have executed
OL,16,Fthe warrant in a "timely manner",
OL,17,Fadding: "They failed to do so at all."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@]O]xD@ROUxD@`O]yD@IOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,FMr Beggs added: "The temporary deputy
OL,7,Fchief constable (Rob) Griffin
OL,8,Fdescribed that failure in his
OL,9,Fstatement as, I quote, a serious,
OL,10,Fsystemic, operational failure on the
OL,11,Fpart of Nottinghamshire Police.
OL,13,F"He recognised the seriousness of what
OL,14,Fhappened, or rather, what didn't
OL,15,Fhappen, and the distress it caused. He
OL,16,Foffered, and we repeat, an unreserved
OL,17,Fapology to the families of the
OL,18,Fdeceased and the survivors."
OL,26,@nD@QOUuD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,FMr Beggs asked the chairwoman of the
OL,7,Finquiry to consider whether it is
OL,8,Frealistic that Calocane would have
OL,9,Fbeen prosecuted, convicted and
OL,10,Fimprisoned at that time while he was
OL,11,Fsuffering with mental illness.
OL,13,FHe added: "We respectfully suggest not
OL,14,Fbut we understand why the bereaved and
OL,15,Fsurvivors are concerned by the failure
OL,16,Fto execute the warrant, and I repeat,
OL,17,Fwe do not seek to defend that failure."
OL,26,@uD@KOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,FHugh Davies KC, representing two
OL,7,FLeicestershire Police officers who
OL,8,Fattended the incident at the warehouse
OL,9,Fweeks before the fatal stabbings, said
OL,10,Fthat an officer did not view records
OL,11,Fof Calocane's previous encounters with
OL,12,Fpolice and if she had done so, "she
OL,13,Fwould have been able to discover that
OL,14,FVC (Valdo Calocane) had an outstanding
OL,15,Fwarrant for his arrest".
OL,17,FMr Davies added: "The officers have
OL,18,Faccepted these shortcomings candidly.
OL,26,@tD@`OUwD@WO]yD@ROU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,F"On behalf of Leicestershire Police,
OL,7,Fthe chief constable apologises for
OL,8,Fthese shortcomings."
OL,10,FMr Beggs said it is Nottinghamshire
OL,11,FPolice's view that the force "did
OL,12,Ftheir reasonable best" to manage
OL,13,FCalocane's interactions with them
OL,14,Fbefore the killings, which include 10
OL,15,Fto 11 incidents, "mostly responding to
OL,16,Frelatively low-level complaints of
OL,17,Fantisocial behaviour".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@TO]sD@^OUtD@VO]wD@ROUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,FHe said that these incidents,
OL,7,Fincluding when he put a university
OL,8,Fflatmate into a headlock and caused a
OL,9,Fwoman to jump out of her window, were
OL,10,Fnot "in any way, unusual or remarkable
OL,11,Ffor the police to have to deal with".
OL,26,@rD@EOUsD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,FThe barrister said that paranoid
OL,7,Fschizophrenia is not a condition that
OL,8,Fpolice officers are trained to manage,
OL,9,Fadding: "Society's answers to these
OL,10,Fpublic safety risks, posed by some
OL,11,Fparanoid schizophrenics, lie
OL,12,Fprincipally not with the police, but
OL,13,Fwith the NHS and other clinical
OL,14,Fservices, where judicious use of the
OL,15,Fmental health legislation may be
OL,16,Frequired."
OL,26,@qD@IOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772019653
OL,3,CPolice could have arrested Nottingham
OL,4,Cattacker months before killings
OL,6,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,7,Findefinite hospital order in January
OL,8,F2024 after admitting manslaughter by
OL,9,Freason of diminished responsibility
OL,10,Fand attempted murder - something which
OL,11,Fhas been widely criticised by the
OL,12,Fvictims' families.
OL,14,FThe chairwoman of the inquiry, who
OL,15,Fwill hear evidence until June this
OL,16,Fyear, will produce a report and
OL,17,Fprovide recommendations in 2027.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
